competitive_positioning.competitive_moat: Technical expertise in GPU-accelerated WebKit fork with deep game industry partnerships
competitive_positioning.differentiation: Pure-GPU HTML renderer specifically optimized for games and native apps across multiple platforms
competitive_advantages: Lightweight WebKit fork optimized for performance
competitive_vulnerabilities: Limited marketing reach vs larger competitors

growth_indicators: Active status with game studio partnerships
growth_bottlenecks: Single-person team limiting sales and support
Long enterprise sales cycles in gaming industry

key_risks: Key person dependency with team of 1
Competition from larger rendering engine providers

strengths: Proven technical solution with game studio validation
High-performance niche with limited direct competitors
concerns: Extremely small team for B2B enterprise sales
Limited total addressable market in gaming UI

next_steps: Expand team to reduce key person risk
